title: Judge blocks California law meant to increase online safety for kids
description: The California Age-Appropriate Design Code probably violates the First Amendment, the judge wrote.

title: Netanyahu, Musk meet at Tesla factory to discuss AI
description: Tech magnate Elon Musk and Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu are meeting in California to discuss AI as each looks to the other to fend off criticism.

title: Regulators struggle to rein in Amazon on safety for warehouse workers
description: After a decade of worker complaints, Amazon’s safety record is under scrutiny from a litany of state and federal regulators. But so far, the company has faced few consequences.

title: Should you update your iPhone to iOS 17? 5 new features to check out
description: Apple’s latest iPhone update, iOS 17, will be available for download today. Here’s a look at the new features and if you should upgrade.
